parameters.text:
=Trend keyword: {{$json.keyword}}
Region: {{$json.region}}
Trend score: {{$json.trendScore}}
Time window: {{$json.timeWindow}}

Task:
Determine whether this trend has AI, institutional, governance, regulatory, security, or education-system relevance.

Guidelines:
- Focus on AI, policy, governance frameworks, regulation, compliance, institutional impact, or strategic implications.
- Exclude consumer hype, entertainment, product launches, or viral trends.
- Be conservative. If institutional relevance is unclear, mark as not relevant.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this exact schema:
{
  "relevant": true or false,
  "relevance_reason": "short explanation",
  "risk_label": "normal" or "sensitive",
  "category": "governance" or "regulation" or "security" or "education"
}

parameters.inputSchema:
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "relevant": {
      "type": "boolean",
      "description": "Whether the trend is relevant to AI governance, regulation, security, or education"
    },
    "relevance_reason": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Short explanation of why the trend is or is not relevant"
    },
    "risk_label": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["normal", "sensitive"],
      "description": "Risk level of the trend"
    },
    "category": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["governance", "regulation", "security", "education"],
      "description": "Primary Enterprise domain category"
    }
  },
  "required": ["relevant", "relevance_reason", "risk_label", "category"],
  "additionalProperties": false
}

